data.description: Don’t miss amazing two unit 3 bed and 2 bath. Situated just beyond the esteemed Russell Woods Subdivision, this exceptional multifamily residence presents two fully independent units, each comprising three generously proportioned bedrooms and two lavish full bathrooms. The array of impressive features is both extensive and remarkable.  The entire residence has undergone comprehensive rewiring, incorporating new electrical systems, and updated plumbing to ensure utmost safety and efficiency. Each unit is equipped with new high-efficiency furnaces and 50-gallon water tanks, guaranteeing a comfortable living environment year-round. The kitchens within both units are designed to cater to the needs of discerning chefs, showcasing top-of-the-line cabinetry, stylish backsplashes, and elegant granite countertops. Stainless steel appliances, including dishwashers, complete these culinary havens.High-end faucets and contemporary lighting fixtures adorn both the kitchens and bathrooms, while recessed lighting throughout the residence adds a touch of sophistication. Each unit features master bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms for enhanced privacy and convenience. The inclusion of new doors and windows throughout the residence contributes to energy efficiency, thereby facilitating savings on utility bills. The bathrooms have been meticulously appointed with new vanities, fixtures, and lighting, evoking a spa-like ambiance. Laminate flooring seamlessly unifies both units. The bedrooms are adorned with top-of-the-line chandeliers and high-end fans, enhancing the sense of opulence and comfort.  Externally, the residence is equally impressive, featuring LED lighting that illuminates the surroundings and security cameras for added peace of mind. Step onto the newly constructed balcony, complete with recessed lighting, and bask in the splendor of the outdoors.  This remarkable multifamily residence not only offers luxurious living but also presents an unparalleled investment opportunity. Whether you opt to occupy one or rent.
